e science fiction film exploring the relationship between humans and artificial intelligence.</p><p>Production is expected to begin in late 2026, with casting announcements scheduled for the coming months.</p><p>Fans reacted positively on social media after the announcement, with many praising the director’s return to the genre that helped launch her career.</p><p>Studio executives believe the film could become one of the biggest releases of the year.</p>','articles/Mq1TzoTosRl40KGrgMlO4PRVWQLrDrU2nabqxOqK.jpg',NULL,1,'manual','2026-05-16 12:31:21','2026-05-16 12:31:21'),(6,8,6,'Award-Winning Director Announces New Science Fiction FilmAward-Winning Director Announces New Science Fiction Film','The acclaimed filmmaker revealed plans for a new science fiction movie set to begin production later this year.','<p>Award-winning director Elena Brooks confirmed that her next project will be a large-scale science fiction film exploring the relationship between humans and artificial intelligence.</p><p>Production is expected to begin in late 2026, with casting announcements scheduled for the coming months.</p><p>Fans reacted positively on social media after the announcement, with many praising the director’s return to the genre that helped launch her career.</p><p>Studio executives believe the film could become one of the biggest releases of the year.</p>','articles/Mq1TzoTosRl40KGrgMlO4PRVWQLrDrU2nabqxOqK.jpg',NULL,1,'manual','2026-05-16 12:31:49','2026-05-16 12:31:49'),(7,7,1,'Local Fashion Brand Expands Into International Markets','The growing fashion company plans to open stores in three new countries by the end of the year.','<p>Popular clothing brand Urban Thread announced plans to expand internationally following strong domestic sales growth over the past two years.</p><p>The company intends to launch retail locations in Singapore, the United Arab Emirates, and the United Kingdom before the holiday shopping season.</p><p>Executives say online demand from overseas customers played a major role in the decision to expand globally.</p><p>Retail analysts note that regional fashion brands are increasingly finding success through social media-driven marketing strategies.</p>','articles/wHa70EEoIy1sX3ZoejCpJGlDtyfcEoN8WYz7Ymb4.jpg',NULL,1,'manual','2026-05-16 12:33:49','2026-05-16 12:33:49'),(8,6,1,'Researchers Develop New Treatment Approach for Diabetes','Scientists say a new experimental treatment may improve blood sugar control for patients with Type 2 diabetes.','<p>Researchers at a leading medical institute have reported promising early results from a clinical trial involving a new diabetes treatment approach.</p><p>The therapy combines medication with personalized nutrition planning and digital monitoring tools to improve long-term blood sugar management.</p><p>Doctors involved in the study say patients experienced more stable glucose levels and fewer complications during the trial period.</p><p>Further testing is expected before the treatment becomes widely available to the public.</p>','articles/FUx2KuUf9gEiZvoyShK7v268Ae5c35K9RpbjgQYC.jpg',NULL,1,'manual','2026-05-16 12:34:17','2026-05-16 12:34:17'),(9,8,7,'Award-Winning Director Announces New Science Fiction FilmAward-Winning Director Announces New Science Fiction Film','The acclaimed filmmaker revealed plans for a new science fiction movie set to begin production later this year.','<p>Award-winning director Elena Brooks confirmed that her next project will be a large-scale science fiction film exploring the relationship between humans and artificial intelligence.</p><p>Production is expected to begin in late 2026, with casting announcements scheduled for the coming months.</p><p>Fans reacted positively on social media after the announcement, with many praising the director’s return to the genre that helped launch her career.</p><p>Studio executives believe the film could become one of the biggest releases of the year.</p>','articles/Mq1TzoTosRl40KGrgMlO4PRVWQLrDrU2nabqxOqK.jpg',NULL,1,'manual','2026-05-16 12:34:34','2026-05-16 12:34:34'),(10,8,8,'Award-Winning Director Announces New Science Fiction Film','The acclaimed filmmaker revealed plans for a new science fiction movie set to begin production later this year.','<p>Award-winning director Elena Brooks confirmed that her next project will be a large-scale science fiction film exploring the relationship between humans and artificial intelligence.</p><p>Production is expected to begin in late 2026, with casting announcements scheduled for the coming months.</p><p>Fans reacted positively on social media after the announcement, with many praising the director’s return to the genre that helped launch her career.</p><p>Studio executives believe the film could become one of the biggest releases of the year.</p>','articles/Mq1TzoTosRl40KGrgMlO4PRVWQLrDrU2nabqxOqK.jpg',NULL,1,'manual','2026-05-16 12:35:29','2026-05-16 12:35:29');
